00:45.621 --> 00:48.146
What're you doing, Sprout, huh?

00:48.673 --> 00:51.853
What are you doing?
Come here, look at you.

00:51.887 --> 00:54.558
Ah.

00:54.592 --> 00:56.527
You gonna walk for me?

00:56.561 --> 00:58.399
You gonna walk for your dad?

00:58.434 --> 01:00.340
Let's try walking again.

01:00.374 --> 01:02.046
There you go.

01:02.080 --> 01:03.914
All right, there you go.

01:03.949 --> 01:07.054
Look at you, big boy now, huh?

01:07.089 --> 01:08.657
There.

01:08.692 --> 01:10.998
See? It's easy.

01:11.033 --> 01:13.789
Huh? Look at you.
(Kisses)

01:14.841 --> 01:17.314
Keep going, keep going.

01:18.917 --> 01:21.658
Sure you want him
to learn to walk so soon?

01:21.694 --> 01:23.968
Well, he's almost a year old.

01:24.002 --> 01:26.587
Faster he learns to walk,
the sooner he learns to march.

01:27.302 --> 01:29.045
That's a good point.

01:29.080 --> 01:31.386
Nah, you're a smart one, Thomas, huh?

01:31.549 --> 01:34.325
Just like your ma, huh?

01:34.359 --> 01:36.163
(Door opens)

01:41.573 --> 01:43.271
Afternoon.

02:04.579 --> 02:07.113
I thought regulars were trained
to fold their own bedding.

02:07.148 --> 02:10.419
He'll be out before Christmas.

02:10.454 --> 02:11.953
They will.

02:11.987 --> 02:15.325
This fighting can't last.

02:15.359 --> 02:18.731
If one redcoat in the house is as
close as it comes to us, then...

02:21.201 --> 02:25.172
then I shall thank the Lord
and be done with it.

02:39.894 --> 02:43.564
(Blade slices)

03:05.530 --> 03:08.798
(Men laughing, chattering)

03:14.308 --> 03:18.479
It's a pity His Majesty don't
pay for scalps no more, huh?

03:18.513 --> 03:20.682
Used to offer 130 cobs a head.

03:20.716 --> 03:23.320
For men, not for boys under 12.

03:23.355 --> 03:24.956
(Men laugh)

03:24.991 --> 03:29.463
That's all Washington
has left to send is boys.

03:30.832 --> 03:32.699
Aye, Major?

03:32.734 --> 03:36.670
Washington coulda had men.
(Urinating)

03:36.705 --> 03:39.476
Coulda had Rangers.

03:40.073 --> 03:44.033
If he were bolder,
not so tight with his purse.

03:44.766 --> 03:48.000
Those pups died for nothing.

